wiki.summary: According to the Rococo Songfacts, in this song, Arcade Fire mock empty-headed feral, modern kids. Multi-instrumentalist Regine Chassagne said: "We recorded it at the church with everyone together in one room, and it spontaneously grew from a small song into something big. At one point the guitars sounded like Nirvana!"
